ed exploration shows how these consolations, taken together, reveal death as a blessing no matter how much we may love life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aDeathxPsychological aspects. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Death & Dying.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016z97831106677140 cprintz978030021925840uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030022470240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300224702423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300224702/original  a978-3-11-066771-4  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY